title: Windows Vista Installation Disk - All Versions of Vista - 32 & 6
description:
This is and ISO image of a Windows Vista Installation Disk that contains all versions of Windows Vista, in 32 and 64 bit arcitechtures. All of them, on one installation disk. Awesome. I did not include anything for getting past the windows activation, such as a keygen or anti-wpa patch, but just select not to activate windows while you are installing, and find something like that later.

I have an extremely fast internet connection, but it's not going to do much good unless you seed when you are done.
